her}}\n|23&ndash;16\n|[[Georgia Dome]] in [[Atlanta]]\n|-\n|January 28, 2001\n|[[Super Bowl XXXV|XXXV]]\n|{{sortname|Brian |Billick}}\n|[[Baltimore Ravens]]\n|{{sort|New York Giants A|[[New York Giants]]}}\n|{{sortname|Jim |Fassel}}\n|{{sort|34&ndash;07|34&ndash;7}}\n|[[Raymond James Stadium]] in [[Tampa, Florida]]\n|-\n|February 3, 2002\n|[[Super Bowl XXXVI|XXXVI]]\n|style=\"background: #00ff7f;\"|{{sortname|Bill| Belichick}}\n|{{sort|New England Patriots A|[[New England Patriots]]}}\n|{{sort|St. Louis Rams B|[[St. Louis Rams]]}}\n|{{sortname|Mike| Martz}}\n|20&ndash;17\n|[[Louisiana Superdome]] in [[New Orleans, Louisiana]]\n|-\n|January 26, 2003\n|[[Super Bowl XXXVII|XXXVII]]\n|style=\"background: #00ff7f;\"|{{sortname|Jon |Gruden}}\n|[[Tampa Bay Buccaneers]]\n|{{sort|Oakland Raiders B|[[Oakland Raiders]]}}\n|{{sortname|Bill |Callahan|Bill Callahan (American football)}}\n|48&ndash;21\n|[[Qualcomm Stadium]] in [[San Diego, California]]\n|-\n|February 1, 2004\n|[[Super Bowl XXXVIII|XXXVIII]]\n|style=\"background: #00ff7f;\"|{{sortname|Bill| Belichick}} (2)\n|{{sort|New England Patriots B|[[New England Patriots]]}}\n|[[Carolina Panthers]]\n|{{sortname|John| Fox|John Fox (football coach)}}\n|32&ndash;29\n|[[Reliant Stadium]] in [[Houston, Texas]]\n|-\n|February 6, 2005\n|[[Super Bowl XXXIX|XXXIX]]\n|style=\"background: #00ff7f;\"|{{sortname|Bill| Belichick}} (3)\n|{{sort|New England Patriots C|[[New England Patriots]]}}\n|{{sort|Philadelphia Eagles B|[[Philadelphia Eagles]]}}\n|style=\"background: #00ff7f;\"|{{sortname|Andy| Reid}}\n|24&ndash;21\n|[[Alltel Stadium]] in [[Jacksonville, Florida]]\n|-\n|February 5, 2006\n|[[Super Bowl XL|XL]]\n|style=\"background: #FFE6BD;\"|{{sortname|Bill |Cowher}}\n|{{sort|Pittsburgh Steelers E|[[Pittsburgh Steelers]]}}\n|{{sort|Seattle Seahawks A|[[Seattle Seahawks]]}}\n|{{sortname|Mike| Holmgren}} [2]\n|21&ndash;10\n|[[Ford Field]] in [[Detroit]], [[Michigan]]\n|-\n|February 4, 2007\n|[[Super Bowl XLI|XLI]]\n|style=\"background: #F